  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">YIRTRAK A.C. / Sustainable development of Rural Communities . The NGO YIRTRAK works for the improvement of the availibility_ quality and treatment of water and forests in rural areas of Chiapas. The aim is to help the local population to adapt sustainable manner of dealing with the natural resources that surround them. The NGO works both with the communities and local schools giving training on the issue. They will also build wood-saving stoves in the villages. The project lasts two years.</narrative>
  </description>
